title: 04/23/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 04/23/21 DPS Best Of
description:
Ross Tucker and the Danettes, filling in for Dan Patrick, discuss the upcoming NFL draft and Tom Brady being upset about players changing jersey numbers with Charles Davis of Yahoo Sports. Adam Lefkoe from NBA on TNT Tuesdays joins the show to share his thoughts on Anthony Davis returning for the Lakers and everything happening around the NBA. And Ohio Congressman Anthony Gonzalez stops by the show to discuss his NIL bill that he is presenting to Congress.
